{
  "video_id": "Ubbmje44gLg",
  "title": "How storytelling helps parents in prison stay connected to their kids | Alan Crickmore",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13500.0,
      "end_time": 14650.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s story time."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15492.0,
      "end_time": 17292.0,
      "text": "Settle back, and I&#39;ll begin."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18643.0,
      "end_time": 23508.0,
      "text": "Once upon a time, a mother duck sat patiently on her nest of eggs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23532.0,
      "end_time": 25265.0,
      "text": "waiting for them to hatch."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25953.0,
      "end_time": 29222.0,
      "text": "And then one day, she felt something move beneath her."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29246.0,
      "end_time": 30555.0,
      "text": "Crack, crack!"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31397.0,
      "end_time": 35813.0,
      "text": "Filled with happiness, she watched as her eggs hatched one by one."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37726.0,
      "end_time": 39917.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know about you, but when I was little,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39941.0,
      "end_time": 43186.0,
      "text": "story time was always one of my favorite parts of the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43210.0,
      "end_time": 46543.0,
      "text": "And I loved reading to my two sons when they were small, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47422.0,
      "end_time": 49490.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s that special time"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49730.0,
      "end_time": 52874.0,
      "text": "when a parent and child can be totally absorbed together"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52898.0,
      "end_time": 55184.0,
      "text": "in mystical kingdoms, fantastical beasties"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55208.0,
      "end_time": 58519.0,
      "text": "or scruffy little ducks that turn out to be swans."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59616.0,
      "end_time": 61926.0,
      "text": "Well, that&#39;s how it is for some children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61950.0,
      "end_time": 63870.0,
      "text": "but for other children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63894.0,
      "end_time": 66710.0,
      "text": "there isn&#39;t a parent around to read to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68930.0,
      "end_time": 70360.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to tell you about Sophie."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 71292.0,
      "end_time": 74616.0,
      "text": "Sophie&#39;s five years old and lives with her parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75982.0,
      "end_time": 78324.0,
      "text": "One day, there&#39;s a bang at the door."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78348.0,
      "end_time": 81133.0,
      "text": "Sophie hears lots of shouting; her mum&#39;s crying."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81157.0,
      "end_time": 84232.0,
      "text": "She sees the police dragging her father away."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84256.0,
      "end_time": 86923.0,
      "text": "Sophie&#39;s afraid. She starts crying, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87574.0,
      "end_time": 89890.0,
      "text": "Weeks go by."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89113.0,
      "end_time": 91764.0,
      "text": "Sophie doesn&#39;t know what&#39;s happened to her dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91788.0,
      "end_time": 93960.0,
      "text": "When she asks her mum, her mum gets upset."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93984.0,
      "end_time": 95774.0,
      "text": "So she stops asking."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97307.0,
      "end_time": 98648.0,
      "text": "Sophie waits."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 99331.0,
      "end_time": 101650.0,
      "text": "She really misses her dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101836.0,
      "end_time": 104947.0,
      "text": "Every day, she hurries home from school, in case he&#39;s come back."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106420.0,
      "end_time": 108909.0,
      "text": "On many nights, she cries herself to sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 111212.0,
      "end_time": 113299.0,
      "text": "Children at school start to tease her."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113323.0,
      "end_time": 114657.0,
      "text": "They call her names."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115300.0,
      "end_time": 119100.0,
      "text": "Somebody&#39;s mum has heard that Sophie&#39;s dad is in prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 120820.0,
      "end_time": 123128.0,
      "text": "Sophie pretends to be ill so she doesn&#39;t have to go to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123749.0,
      "end_time": 126755.0,
      "text": "And her teacher can&#39;t understand why she&#39;s so far behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126779.0,
      "end_time": 128125.0,
      "text": "with her schoolwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 130180.0,
      "end_time": 133863.0,
      "text": "After what seems a long, long time to Sophie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133887.0,
      "end_time": 135379.0,
      "text": "a letter arrives."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135403.0,
      "end_time": 136791.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s from her dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 136815.0,
      "end_time": 139180.0,
      "text": "The writing is very messy."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 139204.0,
      "end_time": 143250.0,
      "text": "The letter makes her mum cry, but she reads a little out to Sophie."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143950.0,
      "end_time": 146884.0,
      "text": "He says that he&#39;s OK and that he&#39;s missing them."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147744.0,
      "end_time": 149770.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a short letter."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150600.0,
      "end_time": 153408.0,
      "text": "Sophie says she&#39;d like to go and see her dad, wherever he is."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153432.0,
      "end_time": 158970.0,
      "text": "But her mum says it&#39;s too far away, and they can&#39;t afford the journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158829.0,
      "end_time": 160979.0,
      "text": "Then one day the phone rings."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161300.0,
      "end_time": 163741.0,
      "text": "\"Sophie, come speak to daddy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 164889.0,
      "end_time": 167809.0,
      "text": "Dad sounds different, far away."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 168571.0,
      "end_time": 170421.0,
      "text": "He says he can&#39;t talk for very long,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 170445.0,
      "end_time": 173452.0,
      "text": "and anyway, it&#39;s very noisy wherever he is."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 173476.0,
      "end_time": 176580.0,
      "text": "And Sophie doesn&#39;t know what to say to him."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 178631.0,
      "end_time": 181392.0,
      "text": "Well, as stories go, that&#39;s not a very nice one."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 181416.0,
      "end_time": 186690.0,
      "text": "In the United Kingdom, 200,000 children"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 186930.0,
      "end_time": 190248.0,
      "text": "experience the shame and isolation of a parent in prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 191117.0,
      "end_time": 193172.0,
      "text": "Two hundred thousand."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 193196.0,
      "end_time": 195506.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s more than the number of children each year"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 195530.0,
      "end_time": 197947.0,
      "text": "who are affected by their parents divorcing."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 198307.0,
      "end_time": 201307.0,
      "text": "And it can affect the children of prisoners very deeply."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 201829.0,
      "end_time": 203420.0,
      "text": "There can be problems at school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 203444.0,
      "end_time": 207411.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re three times more likely to suffer from mental health issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 208932.0,
      "end_time": 210434.0,
      "text": "In so many ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 210458.0,
      "end_time": 215241.0,
      "text": "children are the unintended victims of their parents&#39; crimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 215784.0,
      "end_time": 217315.0,
      "text": "In so many ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 217339.0,
      "end_time": 221403.0,
      "text": "children are the overlooked victims of their parents&#39; crimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223936.0,
      "end_time": 226976.0,
      "text": "Until last November, I was a serving prisoner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 227000.0,
      "end_time": 228499.0,
      "text": "imprisoned for fraud."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 228974.0,
      "end_time": 231573.0,
      "text": "I was dishonest, and I paid the penalty."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 232450.0,
      "end_time": 235674.0,
      "text": "Before that, I&#39;d been a practicing solicitor for 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 236172.0,
      "end_time": 238887.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d had a happy and stable upbringing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238911.0,
      "end_time": 240109.0,
      "text": "a good education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 240133.0,
      "end_time": 243770.0,
      "text": "a happy marriage, which, I&#39;m pleased to say, continues."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 243101.0,
      "end_time": 245648.0,
      "text": "I have two adult sons."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 246387.0,
      "end_time": 249974.0,
      "text": "When they were growing up, I did my best to be around for them"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 249998.0,
      "end_time": 251450.0,
      "text": "as much as I could."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 251474.0,
      "end_time": 253703.0,
      "text": "And I took a careful interest in what they did."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 253727.0,
      "end_time": 256680.0,
      "text": "I read to my boys every night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 256704.0,
      "end_time": 261519.0,
      "text": "and ironically, our favorite story was \"Burglar Bill.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 261543.0,
      "end_time": 263688.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 265210.0,
      "end_time": 267820.0,
      "text": "But when I got to prison, it soon became apparent"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 267844.0,
      "end_time": 271959.0,
      "text": "that my background was very different to that of most of the prisoners."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 272505.0,
      "end_time": 275641.0,
      "text": "Few of the men that I met had had a decent education."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 275665.0,
      "end_time": 280434.0,
      "text": "Indeed, many associated education with humiliation and failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 280458.0,
      "end_time": 284620.0,
      "text": "I can tell you firsthand that prison is dehumanizing."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 285592.0,
      "end_time": 289200.0,
      "text": "Prisoners harden up, they shut down, they close in ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 289863.0,
      "end_time": 291310.0,
      "text": "just to survive."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 292166.0,
      "end_time": 294562.0,
      "text": "And this can be devastating for families."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 296546.0,
      "end_time": 300724.0,
      "text": "In fact, maintaining contact with your family from prison"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 300748.0,
      "end_time": 302681.0,
      "text": "can be very difficult indeed."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 303613.0,
      "end_time": 306763.0,
      "text": "And if a child does get to see their parent in prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 306787.0,
      "end_time": 309897.0,
      "text": "they have to go through the same pat-down searches as the adults."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 309922.0,
      "end_time": 312686.0,
      "text": "They walk through the same detector frames,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 312710.0,
      "end_time": 314871.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re sniffed by the same sniffer dogs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 314895.0,
      "end_time": 318299.0,
      "text": "and all because some children have been the unwitting carriers"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 318323.0,
      "end_time": 320507.0,
      "text": "of drugs and mobile phones."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 321567.0,
      "end_time": 323738.0,
      "text": "And when they get through to see their parent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 323762.0,
      "end_time": 326448.0,
      "text": "they may be tired from a long journey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 326472.0,
      "end_time": 329462.0,
      "text": "shy, tongue-tied, even upset."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 329853.0,
      "end_time": 333424.0,
      "text": "And it isn&#39;t easy for the parents, who may not be getting along."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 334227.0,
      "end_time": 336104.0,
      "text": "For many reasons, not just these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 336957.0,
      "end_time": 341289.0,
      "text": "over half of prisoners lose contact with their children and families."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 341942.0,
      "end_time": 345626.0,
      "text": "How can we help prisoners to stay in contact with their families?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 346574.0,
      "end_time": 348844.0,
      "text": "When I was a prisoner at Channings Wood Prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 348868.0,
      "end_time": 351928.0,
      "text": "I began working for a charity called Storybook Dads."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 352934.0,
      "end_time": 355630.0,
      "text": "Storybook Dads began in 2003,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 355654.0,
      "end_time": 360891.0,
      "text": "when Sharon Berry, a civilian worker in a prison, realized just how much"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 360915.0,
      "end_time": 364128.0,
      "text": "many prisoners wanted to stay in contact with their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 364694.0,
      "end_time": 367360.0,
      "text": "And so, armed with a few storybooks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 367600.0,
      "end_time": 370190.0,
      "text": "she began to help prisoners to read and record stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 370430.0,
      "end_time": 372110.0,
      "text": "to send home to their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 372468.0,
      "end_time": 376272.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t a new idea. Few ideas like this are new."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 376611.0,
      "end_time": 377944.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re great ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 378942.0,
      "end_time": 381970.0,
      "text": "But it was an instant success."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 382466.0,
      "end_time": 387433.0,
      "text": "You may wonder: How does the recording of the stories work in prison?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 387769.0,
      "end_time": 389959.0,
      "text": "Is it difficult for prisoners?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 389983.0,
      "end_time": 391450.0,
      "text": "Can it be challenging?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 393380.0,
      "end_time": 397994.0,
      "text": "Well, the process of choosing, reading and recording a story"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 398180.0,
      "end_time": 400291.0,
      "text": "can be very challenging for prisoners."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 402900.0,
      "end_time": 404109.0,
      "text": "Prison is tough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 404134.0,
      "end_time": 408971.0,
      "text": "and prisoners can&#39;t afford to show any signs of weakness or vulnerability."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 410234.0,
      "end_time": 413248.0,
      "text": "But this, this recording process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 413273.0,
      "end_time": 419265.0,
      "text": "this can be uncomfortable, upsetting, sometimes all just a bit too much."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 421884.0,
      "end_time": 423685.0,
      "text": "And prisoners often cry."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 424741.0,
      "end_time": 429870.0,
      "text": "They cry because they regret missing out on their children&#39;s lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 429701.0,
      "end_time": 433453.0,
      "text": "They cry because they&#39;re ashamed that they&#39;ve let their families down."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 433846.0,
      "end_time": 438544.0,
      "text": "They cry because they don&#39;t know how to go about reading to their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 440298.0,
      "end_time": 445831.0,
      "text": "But because when they come to us we offer a private space, one-to-one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 445855.0,
      "end_time": 448927.0,
      "text": "prisoners don&#39;t need to be tough anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 448951.0,
      "end_time": 451927.0,
      "text": "and they can use their vulnerability as a strength"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 451951.0,
      "end_time": 454351.0,
      "text": "when contacting with their children."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 455977.0,
      "end_time": 458524.0,
      "text": "I remember one prisoner who came to record."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 459950.0,
      "end_time": 462846.0,
      "text": "He was a big, hard man with a reputation for being tough."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 463358.0,
      "end_time": 465699.0,
      "text": "He came along as implacable as ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 465723.0,
      "end_time": 468783.0,
      "text": "But when the door of the recording room closed behind him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 468807.0,
      "end_time": 470551.0,
      "text": "that facade began to crumble."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 470909.0,
      "end_time": 474340.0,
      "text": "From his pocket, he took a screwed-up piece of paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 474590.0,
      "end_time": 475729.0,
      "text": "and quietly began to read the words"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 475753.0,
      "end_time": 479929.0,
      "text": "which he&#39;d written as a message for his two little ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 480555.0,
      "end_time": 482890.0,
      "text": "His hands were shaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 483254.0,
      "end_time": 485561.0,
      "text": "And then, in a surprisingly quiet voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 486572.0,
      "end_time": 489718.0,
      "text": "he began to sing their favorite lullaby."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 490694.0,
      "end_time": 493670.0,
      "text": "You see, there wasn&#39;t much that he could do from behind bars"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 493694.0,
      "end_time": 496836.0,
      "text": "to show his children that he missed and loved them."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 496860.0,
      "end_time": 498476.0,
      "text": "But he could do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 500758.0,
      "end_time": 502726.0,
      "text": "Once the recording is made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 502750.0,
      "end_time": 507266.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s sent to the Storybook Dads production unit"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 507290.0,
      "end_time": 510836.0,
      "text": "at Channings Wood Prison in Devon."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 511258.0,
      "end_time": 512775.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s where I worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 513356.0,
      "end_time": 515794.0,
      "text": "I was trained, along with other prisoners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 515818.0,
      "end_time": 518470.0,
      "text": "to edit and produce recordings sent in"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 518494.0,
      "end_time": 520965.0,
      "text": "from prisons all over the United Kingdom."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 522775.0,
      "end_time": 526823.0,
      "text": "Using audio and video software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 526847.0,
      "end_time": 530775.0,
      "text": "the recordings have the mistakes taken out"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 530799.0,
      "end_time": 533922.0,
      "text": "and sound effects and music added in."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 535467.0,
      "end_time": 541193.0,
      "text": "And the experience and skill which the prison editors gain"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 541217.0,
      "end_time": 543750.0,
      "text": "helps them in their future employment."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 546310.0,
      "end_time": 548801.0,
      "text": "Once the recording is finalized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 548826.0,
      "end_time": 554560.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s transferred to a CD or a DVD and sent out to the families"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 554800.0,
      "end_time": 558253.0,
      "text": "so that the children can watch them whenever they feel the need."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 560260.0,
      "end_time": 564505.0,
      "text": "And they listen to these recordings and watch them a lot --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 566612.0,
      "end_time": 569897.0,
      "text": "at bedtime, in the car ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 569922.0,
      "end_time": 573456.0,
      "text": "Some even take them to school to show their friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 574532.0,
      "end_time": 576127.0,
      "text": "These recordings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 576151.0,
      "end_time": 579527.0,
      "text": "they show the children that they&#39;re loved and missed."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 579954.0,
      "end_time": 581739.0,
      "text": "And they show the prisoner"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 581764.0,
      "end_time": 585922.0,
      "text": "that they can do something for their child, as a parent."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 587375.0,
      "end_time": 589266.0,
      "text": "Do you remember Sophie?"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 589290.0,
      "end_time": 593746.0,
      "text": "Well, one day, just before Christmas, a parcel arrived,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 593770.0,
      "end_time": 595408.0,
      "text": "and this is what was in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 596115.0,
      "end_time": 598345.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s listen to a little of it together."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 598369.0,
      "end_time": 602625.0,
      "text": "(Video) Santa: On, Comet! On, Cupid! On, Donner and Blitzen!"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 602649.0,
      "end_time": 604554.0,
      "text": "Charlie: That&#39;s his reindeer, isn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 604578.0,
      "end_time": 606228.0,
      "text": "Santa: It is his reindeer, yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 606253.0,
      "end_time": 609370.0,
      "text": "Up, up, higher and higher they flew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 609610.0,
      "end_time": 612323.0,
      "text": "across land, across oceans they sped."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 612966.0,
      "end_time": 615910.0,
      "text": "Through the magical northern lights they passed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 615934.0,
      "end_time": 618291.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d love to see the northern lights, wouldn&#39;t you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 618316.0,
      "end_time": 621682.0,
      "text": "Charlie: I figure they&#39;d probably look a bit like that snowman&#39;s belly."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 621706.0,
      "end_time": 623660.0,
      "text": "Santa: They probably would, yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 623684.0,
      "end_time": 625356.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a cool snowman, isn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 625380.0,
      "end_time": 627748.0,
      "text": "Charlie: It&#39;s very cool indeed, I love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 627772.0,
      "end_time": 630152.0,
      "text": "Santa: They visited all the children in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 630176.0,
      "end_time": 632910.0,
      "text": "and left presents for each and every one."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 633611.0,
      "end_time": 637250.0,
      "text": "In the blink of an eye, they were back in Frogsbottom Field."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 637274.0,
      "end_time": 638822.0,
      "text": "(Charlie Laughs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 638846.0,
      "end_time": 640589.0,
      "text": "Santa: You think that&#39;s well funny?"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 640613.0,
      "end_time": 642918.0,
      "text": "Charlie: I want to live in Frogsbottom Field!"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 642942.0,
      "end_time": 645172.0,
      "text": "Santa: Where do you live, in Frogsbottom Tree?"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 645196.0,
      "end_time": 647649.0,
      "text": "Charlie: I don&#39;t, I live in this tree."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 647673.0,
      "end_time": 649744.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve made it all Christmasy-look."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 649768.0,
      "end_time": 650948.0,
      "text": "Santa: It&#39;s nice, that."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 650972.0,
      "end_time": 652581.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve done a good job, good job."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 652605.0,
      "end_time": 654275.0,
      "text": "Charlie: Thank you very much!"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 654299.0,
      "end_time": 656165.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 657957.0,
      "end_time": 660998.0,
      "text": "Alan Crickmore: Sophie and her mum listened to that three times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 661220.0,
      "end_time": 663307.0,
      "text": "and they haven&#39;t laughed so much in a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 663331.0,
      "end_time": 666450.0,
      "text": "They can see that he&#39;s all right, they can see that he loves them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 666474.0,
      "end_time": 669895.0,
      "text": "and the next time he rings, Sophie&#39;s got plenty to talk about:"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 669919.0,
      "end_time": 671846.0,
      "text": "\"What does Charlie the Chimp eat?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 671870.0,
      "end_time": 674428.0,
      "text": "Will daddy do another story very soon?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 675259.0,
      "end_time": 680728.0,
      "text": "Since it began in 2003, Storybook Dads has grown and grown."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 682298.0,
      "end_time": 686550.0,
      "text": "It now operates as Storybook Dads and Storybook Mums"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 686790.0,
      "end_time": 688911.0,
      "text": "in more than 100 prisons in the United Kingdom."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 689506.0,
      "end_time": 693365.0,
      "text": "Ninety-eight percent of the prisoners who take part"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 693389.0,
      "end_time": 696783.0,
      "text": "say that it&#39;s improved their relationship with their child."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 697538.0,
      "end_time": 700284.0,
      "text": "And since 2003,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 700308.0,
      "end_time": 705317.0,
      "text": "over 60,000 DVDs and CDs have been sent out"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 705341.0,
      "end_time": 707670.0,
      "text": "to the children of prisoners."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 710398.0,
      "end_time": 713867.0,
      "text": "For Sophie&#39;s family and for thousands of families like them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 713891.0,
      "end_time": 716272.0,
      "text": "Storybook Dads has been a lifeline."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 717735.0,
      "end_time": 719850.0,
      "text": "Some prisoners say that it&#39;s the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 719874.0,
      "end_time": 723108.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;ve begun to build a relationship with their child."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 723815.0,
      "end_time": 726215.0,
      "text": "And some poor readers have been so inspired"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 726239.0,
      "end_time": 728740.0,
      "text": "by what they&#39;ve been able to achieve"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 728980.0,
      "end_time": 731868.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;ve gone to education classes to improve their own reading skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 734740.0,
      "end_time": 737360.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s go back to the story of \"The Ugly Duckling.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 737610.0,
      "end_time": 742149.0,
      "text": "But this time, I&#39;d like to play you a recording made by a prisoner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 742173.0,
      "end_time": 745439.0,
      "text": "because it encapsulates the power of what we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 746830.0,
      "end_time": 749861.0,
      "text": "The prisoner was an Irish Traveller who couldn&#39;t read."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 751196.0,
      "end_time": 755990.0,
      "text": "And he wanted to send a story home to his daughter for her birthday."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 756595.0,
      "end_time": 759460.0,
      "text": "With the help of a mentor and some clever editing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 759484.0,
      "end_time": 761284.0,
      "text": "something magical happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 762484.0,
      "end_time": 765127.0,
      "text": "This is an extract from the raw recording,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 765151.0,
      "end_time": 770650.0,
      "text": "where the prisoner is reading the story by repeating it, phrase at a time."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 770900.0,
      "end_time": 772100.0,
      "text": "(Audio) Mentor: He had nowhere to hide."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 772340.0,
      "end_time": 773732.0,
      "text": "Owen: He had nowhere to hide."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 773756.0,
      "end_time": 775704.0,
      "text": "Mentor: So one day, he ran away."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 776522.0,
      "end_time": 778831.0,
      "text": "Owen: Then one day, he ran away."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 778855.0,
      "end_time": 782418.0,
      "text": "Mentor: He ran until he came to the great marsh."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 782442.0,
      "end_time": 785171.0,
      "text": "Owen: He run until he come to the great marsh."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 785195.0,
      "end_time": 787481.0,
      "text": "Mentor: Where the wild ducks lived."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 787505.0,
      "end_time": 789705.0,
      "text": "Owen: Where the wild ducks lived."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 791108.0,
      "end_time": 795830.0,
      "text": "AC: And this is a recording -- an excerpt of the recording"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 795855.0,
      "end_time": 801300.0,
      "text": "with the mentor&#39;s voice taken out and sound effects and music added in."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 802690.0,
      "end_time": 804212.0,
      "text": "(Audio) Owen: He had nowhere to hide."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 804236.0,
      "end_time": 806109.0,
      "text": "Then one day, he run away."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 806133.0,
      "end_time": 810702.0,
      "text": "He run until he come to the great marsh where the wild ducks lived,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 810726.0,
      "end_time": 813273.0,
      "text": "and he laid in the rushes for two weeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 813297.0,
      "end_time": 815448.0,
      "text": "(Music) (Ducks quack)"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 815472.0,
      "end_time": 818702.0,
      "text": "Some wild ducks and geese come to look at him."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 818726.0,
      "end_time": 821862.0,
      "text": "\"You&#39;re very ugly,\" they said, and they laughed at him."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 821886.0,
      "end_time": 825180.0,
      "text": "(Ducks quack)"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 828429.0,
      "end_time": 832396.0,
      "text": "The ugly duckling ran away from the great marsh."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 832421.0,
      "end_time": 834198.0,
      "text": "(Duck quacks)"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 836870.0,
      "end_time": 839620.0,
      "text": "AC: And this is how he finished the story:"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 841383.0,
      "end_time": 843859.0,
      "text": "(Audio) Owen: He wasn&#39;t an ugly duckling at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 843883.0,
      "end_time": 848437.0,
      "text": "During the winter, he had grown into a beautiful white swan."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 848939.0,
      "end_time": 853450.0,
      "text": "The other swans looked at him and thought how beautiful he was."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 853485.0,
      "end_time": 855467.0,
      "text": "\"Come with us,\" they said."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 856159.0,
      "end_time": 857310.0,
      "text": "And he did."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 857334.0,
      "end_time": 860364.0,
      "text": "(Bird sounds)"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 864340.0,
      "end_time": 867943.0,
      "text": "Well, Tiara, I hope you have enjoyed this story"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 867967.0,
      "end_time": 871167.0,
      "text": "as much as I enjoyed reading this story to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 872900.0,
      "end_time": 875762.0,
      "text": "I cannot wait to be with you again and hold you in my arms."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 876731.0,
      "end_time": 878731.0,
      "text": "All my love, your daddy, Owen."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 879303.0,
      "end_time": 881604.0,
      "text": "Lots of love, I miss you with all my heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 881628.0,
      "end_time": 883895.0,
      "text": "Goodbye for now, my love. Bye bye."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 884371.0,
      "end_time": 887569.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 891883.0,
      "end_time": 893330.0,
      "text": "(Music ends)"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 894264.0,
      "end_time": 896705.0,
      "text": "AC: When he listened to that recording in his cell"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 896729.0,
      "end_time": 898893.0,
      "text": "before it was sent out to his daughter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 898917.0,
      "end_time": 900148.0,
      "text": "he cried."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 900172.0,
      "end_time": 902613.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s a pretty common reaction from prisoners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 902637.0,
      "end_time": 904444.0,
      "text": "as they realize for the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
